German Army tanks are seen with gun turrets

Variety of German artillery firing including battery of railway guns. Firing done. Smoke seen rising due to firing. German Pz.II and Pz.IV tanks are seen. Huge explosion. Dust rising along with smoke. German aircraft in flight, including JU-87 Stuka dive bombers and Messerschmitt bf 110. Location: Germany. Date:  1940.
